Posts.Content: Apr 24, 2014 02:05PM stevesuitsme wrote: Bless your heart.  I just received results from a call-back today….everything is good.  This has been the longest week of my life!  My head actually hurts from worrying, I do believe.  I am 54 and just had my first mammogram last week….yeah.  I know. Dumb, dumb, dumb.  I feel so silly because the pain wasn't bad at all.  The technicians were absolutely wonderful.  I can't believe I put this off for so long!  I will pray for good results for you.  God bless you.
